isk**: Changing `--without-openssl` to `--without-ssl` is safe\n- **Medium Risk**: Removing TLS support might affect some PROJ features\n- **High Risk**: None identified\n\n**Validation Steps:**\n1. Verify curl configure succeeds with `--without-ssl`\n2. Ensure curl build completes without TLS\n3. Verify libtiff builds successfully\n4. Test complete PROJ build chain\n\n**Historical Context**: This matches Attempt 4 from reflection history which fixed curl directory and hit OpenSSL issue. We're now implementing the solution that Attempt 4 likely used.\n\n**Next Expected Stage**: After fixing curl configuration, expect libtiff build, then PROJ CMake configuration and build."})
